By Bayo Olawunmi  Lagos â€“ Flykite Productions, the organisers of GOtv Boxing Night, on Wednesday announced its decision to postpone the 21st edition of the event (GOtv Boxing Night 21). The show, scheduled to hold on April 2 at the Indoor Sports Hall of the National Stadium, Lagos, will now hold at a date to be announced later. The decision to postpone the event was informed by concerns related to the raging COVID-19 Pandemic.  (NAN)